text: The Fengshan Tiangong Temple () is a temple in Fengshan District, Kaohsiung, Taiwan. ==History== The temple was constructed in 1798. ==Architecture== The temple is a two-story building designed in the Southern Chinese architectural style. ==Transportation== The temple is accessible within walking distance southwest of Dadong Station of the Kaohsiung MRT. ==See also== * List of tourist attractions in Taiwan ==References== Category:1798 establishments in Taiwan Category:Taoist temples in Taiwan Category:Temples in Kaohsiung
title: Fengshan Tiangong Temple
